Organizational Background 
Intelligence Solutions (IS) is focused on the Intelligence Community (IC) offering comprehensive and integrated solutions leveraging our technology and analytics capabilities tuned to IC missions. Intelligence Solutions is focused on maintaining and growing our strong market positions in deployed mission analytics, cyber and information technology while continuing our accelerating transformation as a Digital Systems Integrator aligned with our customers mission needs. We are excited about continuing to add to our dynamic team with this Strategy leadership position. The position is located in Annapolis Junction, Maryland, with the best candidate being well prepared to adapt to dynamic remote and virtual team collaboration as well as travel to customer locations for engagement. 
 
 
 
 
 
